{"tid":2210700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國MI6 賣資料比中國間諜","createTime":"2020-09-20T15:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T16:06:47.000Z","uid":50275,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6551b718bb96b219657e8b03d70d904cb2cb85f8","tid":2210700,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:04:22.000Z","msg":"A British businessman, formerly of MI6, is under investigation for allegedly selling information to undercover spies from China, a Whitehall official says.<br />\n<br />\nFraser Cameron, who runs the EU-Asia Centre think tank, is suspected of passing sensitive information about the EU to two spies allegedly posing as Brussels-based journalists.<br />\n<br />\nHe is alleged to have exchanged the information for thousands of Euros.<br />\n<br />\nBut Mr Cameron told The Times the allegations were &quot;ridiculous&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nThe businessman, who worked for Britain's Secret Intelligence Service from 1976 to 1991, says he has no access to any &quot;secret or confidential information&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nMr Cameron, who has also worked for the Foreign Office and European Commission, told Politico that the allegations &quot;are without foundation&quot;, saying he has &quot;a wide range of Chinese contacts as part of my duties with the EU-Asia Centre and some of them may have a double function&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nA senior Whitehall official, who asked not to be named, told the BBC the investigation had been a long-running joint inquiry between British and Belgian intelligence and claimed that a breakthrough had come in recent months.<br />\n<br />\nHe said this was a great example of how closely British intelligence worked with its European partners.<br />\n<br />\nThe BBC's security correspondent Frank Gardner says there have been growing fears about the extent of covert Chinese intelligence-gathering in Europe, including over sensitive negotiations between the EU and Britain over Brexit."},{"pid":"8f4db5fc211010a9c514d3b7f4742675317c251e","tid":2210700,"uid":286897,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcdf39bd4433ffa1ae21a9663bdceefe6eb45c3e","tid":2210700,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:07:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e458cbc10e54438c074c2fd3017085783fb2f251","tid":2210700,"uid":266294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d348d734af5238f1b7e84da8f20493446b95d01b","tid":2210700,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:09:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c101294bd7107f557fb3098699a0b64b67aae89e","tid":2210700,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf5335dacd19f88fbedbbb66ea49fecf0d0ad5c","tid":2210700,"uid":20563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:17:23.000Z","msg":"The businessman, who worked for Britain's Secret Intelligence Service from 1976 to 1991<br />\n<br />\n今年係咩年份？睇完個on9 topic 唔講以為而家係9幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633b3521fcf579cd85fe7e2ea450e52108049f08","tid":2210700,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T15:25:47.000Z","msg":"Lin 都無你話下年都得架啦"},{"pid":"4b1923538e8e723f0ea3e700239c7ee07cc8d8fb","tid":2210700,"uid":50275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc